<HL>
   Media:
   Three Major TV Networks Will Gamble
   On Live Newscasts in Wee Morning Hours
   ----
   By Kevin Goldman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/07/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<CO>
   CBS CCB GE TBSA TBSB
